                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010520-62-off344 t18010520-62-cd343"></join>, had in his custody and possession a certain Bill of Exchange, as follows:</p>
               <p>Â£27 10s."London, December 27, 1800.</p>

               <p>"One month after date, pay to my order 27l. 10s. for value received. 
