            , at Messrs. Moreau &amp; Co. Barking Church-yard, Tower-street." And afterwards <rs id="t18010520-62-off344" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010520-62-off344" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010520-62-off344" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               did falsely make, forge, and counterfeit, an acceptance in writing, of the same Bill of Exchange
            </rs>, as follows:</p>
               <p>"Accepted, 
               <persName id="t18010520-62-person484">
                  ROBERT 
                  ELVY
               <interp inst="t18010520-62-person484" type="surname" value="ELVY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010520-62-person484" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>
